quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  18,84,"Inna makkanna lahu fee al-ardiwaataynahu min kulli shay-in sababa"
  18,85,"FaatbaAAa sababa"
  18,86,"Hatta itha balaghamaghriba ashshamsi wajadaha taghrubu fee AAaynin hami-atinwawajada AAindaha qawman qulna ya thaalqarnayni imma an tuAAaththiba wa-imma antattakhitha feehim husna"
  18,87,"Qala amma man thalamafasawfa nuAAaththibuhu thumma yuraddu ila rabbihifayuAAaththibuhu AAathaban nukra"
  18,88,"Waamma man amana waAAamila salihanfalahu jazaan alhusna wasanaqoolu lahu minamrina yusra"
  18,89,"Thumma atbaAAa sababa"
  18,90,"Hatta itha balagha matliAAaashshamsi wajadaha tatluAAu AAalaqawmin lam najAAal lahum min dooniha sitra"
  18,91,"Kathalika waqad ahatnabima ladayhi khubra"
  18,92,"Thumma atbaAAa sababa"
  18,93,"Hatta itha balaghabayna assaddayni wajada min doonihima qawman layakadoona yafqahoona qawla"
  18,94,"Qaloo ya tha alqarnayniinna ya/jooja wama/jooja mufsidoona fee al-ardi fahalnajAAalu laka kharjan AAala an tajAAala baynanawabaynahum sadda"
  18,95,"Qala ma makkannee feehi rabbeekhayrun faaAAeenoonee biquwwatin ajAAal baynakum wabaynahum radma"
  18,96,"Atoonee zubara alhadeedi hattaitha sawa bayna asadafayni qalaonfukhoo hatta itha jaAAalahu naran qalaatoonee ofrigh AAalayhi qitra"
  18,97,"Fama istaAAoo an yathharoohuwama istataAAoo lahu naqba"
